          <div class="legcap"><span><b>Gezi:</b> Buckingham → St James's Park → South Bank → London Eye → SEA LIFE. Çoğu yürüme.</span><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://www.google.com/maps/dir/?api=1&origin=51.501364,-0.14189&destination=51.5040437,-0.1181412&waypoints=51.5007292,-0.1246254%7C51.5031864,-0.1195192%7C51.501558,-0.119506&travelmode=walking">Aç →</a></div>
        </div>
